These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, skateboard, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Transport        | tram | snowmobile   | trike | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, bike, bus
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the scooter is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the scooter is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Transport   | bus    | scooter | bike | snowmobile    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: domino, poker, scrabble, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Game          | monopoly | scrabble | poker    | domino      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
City: new-york, liverpool, edinburgh, san-francisco
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| City   | edinburgh       | new-york   | liverpool    | san-francisco  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, animation, comedy, disaster
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the indian is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | drama    | comedy   | disaster       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

