.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
4 different games are played: domino, backgammon, snooker, monopoly
1. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Game   | monopoly | backgammon     | domino  | snooker  |

