.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
4 different pets are kept: pony, chinchilla, lizard, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | lizard  | pony     | chinchilla |

