.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, chess, mah-jongg
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the person playing chess##2
4. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
5. the person playing chess is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | canasta   | snooker | chess |
| Pet    | turtle     | hamster | cat     | mouse  |

