.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, cauliflower, nectarine, asparagus
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. the person eating pineapple is the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of disco and the person eating nectarine##2
4. the person eating pineapple is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Food      | cauliflower       | nectarine   | pineapple | asparagus |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, doctor, entrepreneur, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, paramedic-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the chef##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is paramedic-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is paramedic-polo is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
5. the doctor is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Job   | chef   | paramedic   | doctor      | entrepreneur      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | paramedic-polo | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, mah-jongg, backgammon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, hip-hop, soul
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
3. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
4. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the fan of disco and the fan of hip-hop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game          | backgammon | monopoly  | mah-jongg  | billiard |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | hip-hop | ambient | disco   |

