.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, family, satire, thriller
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bolivar, tiparillo, bluemaster
1. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
4. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama | satire | thriller  |
| Cigar     | bolivar   | oliveros  | bluemaster  | tiparillo |

