.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, kiwi, pineapple, cherry
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goat, snake
1. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating cherry is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
6. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Food   | pineapple | cherry | blueberry | kiwi |
| Pet           | snake     | dog     | goat   | frog         |

