.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, airplane, trike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
5. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Transport   | subway | taxi | airplane    | trike |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

