.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, gardening, sudoku
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, blood-red, purple, fuchsia
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
5. the person who likes blood-red is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes purple##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | gardening | board-games | chess    |
| Color   | purple | blood-red  | fuchsia     | orange |

