.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
House: farmhouse, colonial, victorian, futuristic
There 4 different types of food: corn, kale, pepper, strawberry
1. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
3. the futuristic house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
7. the person eating corn is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| House   | futuristic | farmhouse    | victorian       | colonial |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

