.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
House: cape-cod, cottage, victorian, craftsman
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the cottage house is in an even position##4
2. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the cape-cod house and the person driving the helicopter##2
4. the cottage house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| House         | cape-cod | victorian   | craftsman | cottage |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 